R - B says acquires Peerless Industrial . R - B Capital Corp said it acquired control of Peerless Industrial Group Inc . R - B said its cash tender offer for all Peerless shares expired May 15 . More than six million Peerless common and Class B shares , represented 97 . 1 - percent of the total outstanding , were tendered and accepted , R - B said . R - B said it will pay $ 1 . 67 for each share of Peerless that was not purchased in the tender offer . ( ( - - Chicago Newsdesk 312 - 408 - 8787 ) ) 
